OL,3,CFamily's anger after severely autistic
OL,4,Cwoman offered dementia care home place
OL,6,FThe couple, in their 70s, applied to
OL,7,FNorth East Lincolnshire Council for
OL,8,Faccommodation at the Rock Foundation
OL,9,Fin Caistor, a charity for adults with
OL,10,Flearning disabilities which Sophie has
OL,11,Fbeen attending for almost 20 years.
OL,13,FThey were told she met the
OL,14,Frequirements for supported living.
OL,16,FBut the council rejected their
OL,17,Fapplication, saying funding could not
OL,18,Fbe provided because the Rock
OL,19,FFoundation crosses the North East
OL,20,FLincolnshire county border.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
