OL,3,CFamily's anger after severely autistic
OL,4,Cwoman offered dementia care home place
OL,6,FInstead they provided a list of
OL,7,Falternatives, 16 of which were
OL,8,Fdementia care homes.
OL,10,F"It was just awful", said Pat. "Sophie
OL,11,Fis not a dementia case, she likes to
OL,12,Fdo things, she likes to be active,
OL,13,Fdrawing and doing artwork.
OL,15,F"We did go look around a few and they
OL,16,Fwere for old people with dementia.
OL,17,FThey were totally unsuitable for
OL,18,FSophie."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
