OL,3,CFamily's anger after severely autistic
OL,4,Cwoman offered dementia care home place
OL,6,FDick added: "There was no empathy.
OL,7,FLetting your children go at any stage
OL,8,Ffor any parent is a big thing. When
OL,9,Fyou feel that you're kicking someone
OL,10,Fout who is vulnerable is difficult to
OL,11,Ftalk about.
OL,13,F"We're very protective of Sophie so we
OL,14,Fwant what's right for her. And the
OL,15,FRock Foundation is perfect."
OL,17,F'They're not looking at the person'
