OL,6,FCouncils in England spend on average
OL,7,Fmore than a third of their budgets on
OL,8,Fadult social care, with more than #22
OL,9,Fbillion expected to be spent in 2024/
OL,10,F25, according to the Association of
OL,11,FDirectors of Adult Social Services
OL,12,F(ADASS).
OL,14,FSophie's parents believe the decision
OL,15,Fto reject Sophie's claim comes down to
OL,16,Fmoney.
OL,18,FThe Rock Foundation has 12 beds
OL,19,Favailable, but four currently stand
OL,20,Fempty.
