OL,4,Cwoman offered dementia care home place
OL,6,FFounder Pam Hodge said three are for
OL,7,Fpeople like Sophie, who are waiting on
OL,8,F"bureaucratic decisions".
OL,10,F"I think it's all about policies and
OL,11,Fprocedures and they're not looking at
OL,12,Fthe person," she said.
OL,14,F"At the end of the day, I'm a parent
OL,15,Fand I want them to experience the
OL,16,Fthings all our other children can
OL,17,Fexperience.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
