OL,6,F"Instead of putting them in a home for
OL,7,Fdementia or a home for people with
OL,8,Fmental health problems. They don't
OL,9,Fneed that. They need to be somewhere
OL,10,Fwhere they can live life to the full."
OL,12,FA North East Lincolnshire Council
OL,13,Fspokesperson said: "In North East
OL,14,FLincolnshire, we commission
OL,15,Forganisations to deliver adult social
OL,16,Fcare services on our behalf. We work
OL,17,Fclosely with these organisations to
OL,18,Fmake sure that local people have
OL,19,Faccess to good quality care to suit
OL,20,Ftheir needs.
